====================
QL Windows Installer
====================

Requirements:

* 7zip
* wine (tested with 1.6.1)
* QL build deps
* wget
* mercurial
* 1.5GB free space

How To
------

* Run build_installer.sh
* _bin will be created which contains installers of various dependencies
* _build_env will be created which will contain the installer once finished


SDK Environment
---------------

After running build_installer.sh, _build_env/quodlibet-win-sdk contains
a development environment including all dependencies, a repository clone
and the needed launchers.
